OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy and
OL,6,Fmurky evening in the west with some
OL,7,Fmist and patchy drizzle at first.
OL,8,FMainly dry around the Moray Firth with
OL,9,Fsome late bright then clear spells.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FMainly dry with early
OL,12,Fmorning cloud soon burning off to
OL,13,Fleave a warm and sunny day. However
OL,14,Fstaying rather cloudy for western
OL,15,Fcoasts where the odd light shower is
OL,16,Fpossible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
