OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FPartly cloudy but warm with the risk
OL,7,Fof heavy and thundery outbreaks of
OL,8,Frain on Thursday and Friday. Turning
OL,9,Ffresher by Saturday with the risk of a
OL,10,Ffew showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
